        i0.ɵɵelementStart(155, "p", 19);
        i0.ɵɵtext(156, " Even if the Athenians did banish him, very soon after his death they honored him as no other mortal. They built a great tomb for him and decreed that it should be forever a sanctuary for slaves and for all poor and helpless people, in memory of one who through his life had been the protector of the defenseless ");
